I89. Selection procedure

I11(a) T4In GeneralK._These procedures apply to the procurement of architectural and engineering services by an agency head.

I11(b) T4Annual StatementsK._The agency head shall encourage firms to submit annually a statement of qualifications and performance data.

I11(c) T4EvaluationK._For each proposed project, the agency head shall evaluate current statements of qualifications and performance data on file with the agency, together with statements submitted by other firms regarding the proposed project. The agency head shall conduct discussions with at least 3 firms to consider anticipated concepts and compare alternative methods for furnishing services.

