I11(b) T4Assistance for Demonstrations of Enterprise Development._

I12(1) T4In generalK._The Commission may provide assistance under this section for demonstrations of enterprise development, including site acquisition or development where necessary for the feasibility of the project, in connection with the development of the region's energy resources and the development and stimulation of indigenous arts and crafts of the region.

I12(2) T4Cooperation by federal agenciesK._In carrying out the purposes of this subtitle and in implementing this section, the Secretary of Energy, the Environmental Protection Agency, and other federal agencies shall cooperate with the Commission and shall provide assistance that the Federal Cochairman may request.

I12(3) T4Available amountsK._In any fiscal year, not more than_

I13(A) $3,000,000 shall be obligated for energy resource related demonstrations; and

I13(B) $2,500,000 shall be obligated for indigenous arts and crafts demonstrations.

Q04

