I11(a) T4Initial MeetingK._Each Commission shall hold an initial meeting not later than 180 days after the date of the enactment of this section.

I11(b) T4Annual MeetingK._Each Commission shall conduct at least 1 meeting each year with the Federal Cochairperson and at least a majority of the State members present.

I11(c) T4Additional MeetingsK._Each Commission shall conduct additional meetings at such times as it determines and may conduct such meetings by electronic means.

