I89. Approval of applications for assistance

I11(a) T4Evaluation by State MemberK._An application to a Commission for a grant or any other assistance for a project under this subtitle shall be made through, and evaluated for approval by, the State member of the Commission representing the applicant.

I11(b) T4CertificationK._An application to a Commission for a grant or other assistance for a project under this subtitle shall be eligible for assistance only on certification by the State member of the Commission representing the applicant that the application for the project_

I12(1) describes ways in which the project complies with any applicable State economic and infrastructure development plan;

I12(2) meets applicable criteria under section 15504;

I12(3) adequately ensures that the project will be properly administered, operated, and maintained; and

I12(4) otherwise meets the requirements for assistance under this subtitle.

