I12(2) T4Exceptions._

I13(A) T4Administrative expenses of local development districtsK._The funding prohibition under paragraph (1) shall not apply to grants to fund the administrative expenses of local development districts under section 15505.

I13(B) T4Multicounty and other projectsK._A Commission may waive the application of the funding prohibition under paragraph (1) with respect to_

I14(i) a multicounty project that includes participation by an attainment county; and

